        "The config package exposes mutable package-level process state (`BasePath`, `Architecture`, `DebugMode`, `Ready`, `DockerDir`) in `goseg/config/bootstrap.go`, while a higher-level context abstraction (`RuntimeContext` and `RuntimeContextSnapshot`) exists in `goseg/config/config.go` but is not consistently used by orchestration constructors.",
        "`goseg/docker/orchestration/container_bridge.go` has a global-seeking constructor (`llamaRuntimeFromGlobals`) that reads `config.DockerDir`/`config.UrbitsConfig` directly, alongside other constructors that use dependency-injected runtime fields.",
        "The startram backup area adds thin local pass-through wrappers (`encryptFile`/`decryptFile`) instead of owning one clear API boundary."
      ],
      "impact_scope": "subsystem",
      "fix_scope": "architectural_change",
      "confidence": "high"
    }
